Subject: [patch] softirq preemption: optimization
From: Ingo Molnar <mingo@elte.hu>
optimize softirq preemption by allowing a hardirq context to pick up
softirq processing.
Signed-off-by: Ingo Molnar <mingo@elte.hu>
---
